# OpenWiki maintains an AGENTS.md (the non-Claude counterpart to CLAUDE.md);
# this project keeps it untracked so `openwiki code --update` (locally or in
# CI) never commits it. CLAUDE.md, by contrast, is tracked and its OPENWIKI
# block rides along in the docs PR.
AGENTS.md
